## Infrastructure tools (mandatory routing)

Before any infra CLI, skill, or MCP action, read **`.cursor/rules/infras/tools.mdc`** and use **only** listed tools:

| Goal | Primary tool | Also see |
|------|--------------|----------|
| Author, validate, plan, apply AWS resources | **Terraform** (`infra/aws/aws_tf/`) | **`iac/terrafrom.mdc`**, **`.cursor/skills/tf/SKILL.md`** |
